    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>Tenderstem broccoli </strong>in half</p><p>Zest <strong>half </strong>your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lemon[s]</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Cut your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> into 1 slice per person</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
