    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halved broccoli</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once tender, add the <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>and <strong>lemon zest </strong>to the pan and cook for 1-2 min further or until fragrant – this is your <strong>garlic & lemon broccoli</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
