      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the orzo is cooked through, add the <strong>drained butter beans </strong>with your <strong>soft cheese</strong>, most<strong> </strong>of your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(save some for garnish!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min or until the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>butter bean & orzo cacio e pepe</strong></p>",
