      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>butter bean & orzo cacio e pepe </strong>with the <strong>garlic & lemon broccoli </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon slice </strong>and top the orzo with the <strong>toasted pine nuts</strong>, <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
